{"id":580719,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【真理部】两会蓝衣女记者/","date":"2018-03-13T17:00:54Z","modified":"2018-03-15T05:54:08Z","title":"【真理部】禁止媒体人员讨论两会蓝衣女记者事件","content":"<p>紧急通知：所有媒体人员禁止在社交平台讨论两会蓝衣女记者事件，已发布的删除。网站一律不得炒作此事件。</p>\n<p>【“真理部”是网民对中国共产党中央委员会宣传部和其下属的各省宣传部，以及国家级的国务院新闻办公室，中央文明办，国家广播电影电视总局，出版总署，文化部等一系列言论出版审查机构的总称。】</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/zhenlibu2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-186236\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/zhenlibu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/zhenlibu2.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/10/zhenlibu2-300x65.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-580730\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/2018-03-13-2-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/2018-03-13-2-300x292.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/2018-03-13-2.png 607w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E6%8F%90%E9%97%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%99%BD%E7%9C%BC%E9%84%99%E8%A7%86/\">【弄个大新闻】两会红与蓝：白眼翻出假外媒</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%E3%80%90%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%AF%8D%E5%BA%93%E3%80%91%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E7%BF%BB%E7%99%BD%E7%9C%BC%E9%81%AD%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD-%E8%93%9D%E8%A1%A3%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E6%88%90%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%AF%8D/\">【敏感词库】两会翻白眼遭屏蔽 蓝衣记者成敏感词</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>中国数字空间｜</strong><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/2018%E4%BF%AE%E5%AE%AA%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6\">2018修宪</a></st